00:25:02.140 --> 00:25:02.660
Yixi,

00:25:02.800 --> 00:25:04.250
ito ang sikat na ulam ng Wanfeng Kingdom...

00:25:09.359 --> 00:25:09.960
Yixi?

00:25:16.319 --> 00:25:16.920
Yixi!

00:25:31.720 --> 00:25:32.240
Yixi?

00:25:42.619 --> 00:25:43.259
Yixi.

00:25:44.299 --> 00:25:44.779
Yixi!

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:45.839
Ako ito, Chen.

00:25:46.359 --> 00:25:46.799
Yixi,

00:25:47.759 --> 00:25:49.039
labanan ang Night Deity.

00:25:49.400 --> 00:25:49.839
Yixi!

00:25:58.500 --> 00:25:59.259
Kung ito

00:26:00.200 --> 00:26:01.599
makapagpapaginhawa sa iyong paghihirap,

00:26:02.460 --> 00:26:03.339
magtitiis ako

00:26:04.140 --> 00:26:05.019
gaano man karami ang iyong kunin.

00:26:13.019 --> 00:26:13.619
Yixi,

00:26:15.359 --> 00:26:16.700
kahit gaano ka pa magbago,

00:26:18.140 --> 00:26:19.619
Palagi kitang makikilala.

00:26:21.019 --> 00:26:21.980
Dahil alam ko

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.480
hindi mo ako sasaktan.

00:26:32.119 --> 00:26:32.759
Yixi!

00:26:52.500 --> 00:26:53.099
anong mali?

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:54.299
Bangungot?

00:26:57.420 --> 00:26:57.980
ayos lang ako.

00:26:59.059 --> 00:27:00.180
Pero nararamdaman ko

00:27:00.819 --> 00:27:02.980
ang kapangyarihan ng Night Deity sa loob ko
ay mas mahirap kontrolin.

00:27:03.579 --> 00:27:05.500
Hindi ko alam kung kailan ito mawawala

00:27:06.140 --> 00:27:06.980
at saktan ka ulit.

00:27:08.579 --> 00:27:09.220
Chen,

00:27:10.819 --> 00:27:11.940
Takot na takot ako.

00:27:12.940 --> 00:27:15.059
Natatakot akong maubos ko ito ng buo

00:27:15.900 --> 00:27:17.019
at nawala sa isip ko.

00:27:18.059 --> 00:27:20.619
Baka sakaling makalimutan ko ang lahat
sa pagitan natin.

00:27:20.619 --> 00:27:21.019
Hindi kailanman.

00:27:22.900 --> 00:27:23.539
Kasama ko dito,

00:27:24.940 --> 00:27:26.500
hindi mo haharapin ang lahat ng ito ng mag-isa.

00:27:28.900 --> 00:27:30.900
Maghahanda ako ng mga pampakalma na halamang gamot.

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:32.460
Huwag kang matakot.

00:27:33.700 --> 00:27:34.740
Malalampasan natin ito.

00:27:53.888 --> 00:27:55.119
Oo. Siya yun!

00:27:56.380 --> 00:27:56.780
Noon,

00:27:57.019 --> 00:27:58.259
Nakita ko yung babae

00:27:58.579 --> 00:27:59.168
ay parang...

00:28:01.539 --> 00:28:02.900
"Sobrang sakit."

00:28:03.319 --> 00:28:05.279
"Hayaan mong kagatin kita."

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:09.720
Ang Diyus ng Gabi

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:11.799
naubos ang lakas ng buhay niya noon.

00:28:12.079 --> 00:28:13.200
Nakita ko ito ng sarili kong mga mata.

00:28:13.279 --> 00:28:14.440
Walang duda tungkol dito!

00:28:14.599 --> 00:28:15.440
Wan Guchen,

00:28:16.319 --> 00:28:19.319
ang lakas ng loob mong dalhin si Bai Yixi,
ang demonyong iyon, sa Wanfeng Kingdom!

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:22.799
Isinapanganib mo ang lahat ng buhay ng kaharian.

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:24.920
Isa ka talagang sumpa!

00:28:24.920 --> 00:28:26.359
Eksakto! Isang halimaw!

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:27.000
Isang sumpa!

00:28:27.599 --> 00:28:28.079
Tama!

00:28:28.559 --> 00:28:29.559
Alam mong sinumpa ka,

00:28:29.839 --> 00:28:30.599
bumalik pa!

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:31.559
At kahit ikaw

00:28:31.600 --> 00:28:32.599
nagdala ng demonyo sa iyo.

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:34.480
Ito ay sinadya!

00:28:34.480 --> 00:28:36.440
Paano
nagagawa ng maharlikang pamilya ang gayong karumihan!

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:37.759
Puro kasamaan!

00:28:38.359 --> 00:28:40.640
Walang awang pumapatay ang Night Deity.

00:28:40.799 --> 00:28:42.400
Isang sulyap sa kanya

00:28:43.000 --> 00:28:44.359
at patay ka ng madaling araw.

00:28:44.799 --> 00:28:45.920
Ano ang dapat nating gawin?

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:50.940
Sinapian siya ng Night Deity.

00:28:51.700 --> 00:28:52.700
Siya ay inosente.

00:28:54.599 --> 00:28:56.819
Kung alam niyang ang Night Deity
ay natatakan sa loob niya,

00:28:57.099 --> 00:28:58.380
hindi siya dapat gumala.

00:28:59.420 --> 00:29:01.660
Tunay na inosente ang mga pinatay niya.

00:29:01.660 --> 00:29:02.180
Eksakto!

00:29:02.220 --> 00:29:02.740
Magaling sinabi!

00:29:04.740 --> 00:29:05.339
Iresponsable!

00:29:06.740 --> 00:29:07.460
Sapat na usapan.

00:29:07.940 --> 00:29:08.740
arestuhin siya

00:29:09.339 --> 00:29:10.859
at pagkatapos ay sakupin si Bai Yixi.

00:29:11.539 --> 00:29:12.180
Kunin sila!

00:29:21.680 --> 00:29:22.279
Xiaochuan!

00:29:22.900 --> 00:29:23.779
Huwag mo siyang sasaktan!

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:29.039
Xiaochuan!

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:33.440
Ina, hindi ko akalain na masama siya.

00:29:33.440 --> 00:29:36.240
Ang pagkakaroon ng demonyong natatakan sa loob ay nakakalungkot.

00:29:36.440 --> 00:29:38.519
Wala ka namang papatayin diba?

00:29:40.359 --> 00:29:41.160
pangako ko

00:29:42.079 --> 00:29:43.200
hindi kami papatay.

00:29:48.660 --> 00:29:49.099
Xiaochuan!

00:29:50.039 --> 00:29:50.720
nasaan siya?

00:29:52.240 --> 00:29:53.680
Mga walang kwentang tanga!

00:30:05.839 --> 00:30:06.480
Yixi!

00:30:07.220 --> 00:30:07.660
Yixi!

00:30:11.339 --> 00:30:11.819
Yixi!

00:30:13.180 --> 00:30:13.940
Yixi, anong meron?

00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:16.360
Ang lakas ng demonyo ay sumiklab?

00:30:17.380 --> 00:30:17.900
Yixi.

00:30:18.976 --> 00:30:20.299
Huwag mo akong ikulong. Papasukin mo ako.

00:30:20.299 --> 00:30:20.980
matutulungan kita!

00:30:22.259 --> 00:30:22.819
Yixi!

